Message: The user completes the submission of the form
Hello, I would like to know how long it takes for a campaign to be approved?
Hi there! The ad approval process usually takes between 1-2 business days. Sometimes it can be even quicker, thanks to our awesome Ad Ops team! If you have any other questions, feel free to ask.
will I receive any notification if approved?
Yes, you will receive a notification once your ads are approved and live. If you have any other questions or need further assistance, just let me know!
is there a minimum daily value for ads?
Could you please clarify if you are asking about the minimum daily budget required for running ads on our platform? This will help me provide you with the most accurate information.
no, i'd like to know if my raster is correct
Sure, I can help with that! Could you please provide more details about the platform or service you're using for your raster? This will help me give you the most accurate guidance.

Thanks for providing the details! To check if your raster is correct, please make sure you have followed all the steps in creating your ad. You can refer to this article for guidance on creating your first ad: [How to create your first ad](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/17618196971149-How-to-create-your-first-ad). If you need further assistance, feel free to ask!
